rows.label: qst500105_msg0002
rows.name:
This quite rare encounter.
Temimi not meet person who not
Nopon or Tirkin for long time.

rows.label: qst500105_msg0003
rows.name:
Friends tell Temimi about latest politics
and trends of fashion in world outside?

rows.label: qst500105_msg0004
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh! Wait-wait-wait!
Temimi just remember why Temimi
come here in first place!

rows.label: qst500105_msg0005
rows.name:
Temimi come to Superbia in search
of tasty-tasty ingredients for juice!

rows.label: qst500105_msg0006
rows.name:
But Temimi lose all money betting on
Chooby Tubes in Alba Margen.
Temimi land in debt bigger than big.

rows.label: qst500105_msg0007
rows.name:
Tirkin offer to hire Temimi, so Temimi
end up living lazy life here where food
and clothes and bed provided...

rows.label: qst500105_msg0008
rows.name: But that not right at all!

rows.label: qst500105_msg0009
rows.name:
Temimi must grab random ingredient
from Superbia and take back to
other brothersisterpons in Avaritia!

rows.label: qst500105_msg0010
rows.name: Thank you for talk to Temimi!

rows.label: qst500105_msg0011
rows.name:
Maybe Temimi's other brotherpons
and sisterpons in trouble too. They all
searching for ingredients as well.

rows.label: qst500105_msg0012
rows.name:
If friends meet them sometime,
say hello-lo like to Temimi!
